<div class="com-share" data-id="2048" data-title="《（超）扁平》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2048/medium/2048.jpg?1436647593" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2048" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
